book:
Haru PDF
haru



 &reftitle.intro;


  The PECL/haru extension provides bindings to the libHaru library.
  libHaru is a free, cross platform, and Open Source library for generating
  PDF files.



  The Haru library (libHaru) may be found here:
  &url.haru.lib;.

